content:
Einstein Discovery prepares your model, analyzes your data, and displays its progress along the way. Einstein Discovery stories are now models. The model provides a list of variables, insights, and charts that are ranked according to their impact on the selected outcome variable.

When finished, Einstein opens the new model. In addition, Einstein Discovery determines their level of interest and relevance to the outcome. Your new model is added to the list of models to which you have access. If saved to a shared app, users with access to that app also have access to your model.
